sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Iniciador
  participant CA as Cliente A
  participant S as ChatServer
  participant CS as CallService
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant CB as Cliente B
  participant CC as Cliente C
  participant U as UdpRelayServer

  A->>CA: Inicia videollamada grupal
  CA->>S: call:start
  S->>CS: start(userId, groupId)
  CS->>DB: verifica llamada activa
  CS->>DB: crea call + participants
  CS-->>CB: call:incoming
  CS-->>CC: call:incoming
  CS-->>CA: call:updated
  Note over CB,CC: Cada invitado decide individualmente.
  CB->>S: call:accept
  S->>CS: accept(B)
  CS->>DB: B = joined, call = in_progress
  CS-->>CA: call:updated
  CS-->>CB: call:updated
  CS-->>CC: call:updated (sigue invited)
  CC->>S: call:reject
  S->>CS: reject(C)
  CS->>DB: C = rejected
  Note over CC: La barra del grupo permanece visible con "Unirse".
  CC->>S: call:join
  S->>CS: join(C)
  CS->>DB: C = joined
  CA->>U: audio/video UDP
  U-->>CB: media solo a joined
  U-->>CC: media solo a joined
  CB->>U: audio/video UDP
  U-->>CA: media
  CC->>S: call:end
  CS->>DB: C = left
  Note over CA,U: La llamada termina cuando no queda ningún participante joined.
